{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348610/extras/slime3kdiscord__1_.gif?t=1733128800\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A blob of goo used to create artificial humans has become sentient and risen up against its creator \u2014 the Despot, an evil AI and (unfortunately) ruler of the world in the year 3000! Become this murderous jelly and pave your path with death, violence and pretzels in this action-packed roguelite from the creators of Despot's Game and Despotism 3K. We tried to blatantly clone games like Vampire Survivors, Halls of Torment, Brotato, Soulstone Survivors and 20 Minutes Till Dawn, but our crazy experiments went too far. By introducing a shop straight out of AutoChess and some TCG deckbuilding mechanics to the familiar formula, we created what we've dubbed our perfect abomination: Slime 3K.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \u00a0<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348610/extras/slime-steam.gif?t=1733128800\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DECKBUILDING MEETS MEATGRINDING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slime 3K adds strategic depth and more creative experimentation to the survivor-like formula by introducing a deep deckbuilding system. Unlock, upgrade, mix and match your cards to stock up an impressive arsenal of zany weapons and traits. Create the perfect bloodbath loadout for each run! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348610/extras/slime_tags_swipe_animation2_wip.gif?t=1733128800\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SURVIVE THE ONSLAUGHT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your enemies get stronger every minute, and so should you! Explore tons of fun approaches to good ol' annihilation \u2014 electrocute everyone, throw acid on the floor, mow down puny humans with an AK-47, summon zombies, or throw explosive watermelons!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348610/extras/violence-4.gif?t=1733128800\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GOTTA BLOB 'EM ALL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to take on every creation the mad Despot can come up with: knights, mutants, cyborg abominations, ballerinas, stilt acrobats, carnivorous tomatoes, and Despot knows what else. The tiny pink humans make such a satisfying pop when you crush them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348610/extras/SLIDE_4.gif?t=1733128800\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Punycide","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2348610/6478cb7743d2e0348387ee39ddf2e433cfdf7c1f.jpg"},{"name":"Two Towers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2348610/385422018b874e326d7312f758011c97b8c91d19.jpg"},{"name":"Bloody Swan Lake","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2348610/a1bf879f574733b74782bf6b22cf6140aa2d0fb4.jpg"},{"name":"Poke the Hive","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2348610/87aaa8e462c98f53067663a1961921df27f21a6c.jpg"},{"name":"Hunter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2348610/82b6f28c8e1c6147085b37293f608a6b742df26f.jpg"},{"name":"Anti-Mage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2348610/b638c14ca7f948524f84e64519aca3b0648aa119.jpg"},{"name":"Anti-Maniac","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2348610/86ccd6eaebcefe7c796cb4f2fd22a28231dd65ab.jpg"},{"name":"Tournament Champion","path